This script written for Greek studends (ages 12-16).
Point is:
- First try of Slackware Linux installation.(format disks gdisk,create root passwd,edit files in /etc, setup user account, groups etc..)
* First try to install a linux.iso in QEMU using terminal.(what is the terminal use and power)
+ To play (edit) with the script and customise it at home.(create their own simple script no matter if its running properly but learn how to use shellcheck)

